            <title>[KAFKA-5700] producer missed header information when splitting batches</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-5700</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In `ProducerBatch.tryAppendForSplit`, invoking `this.recordsBuilder.append(timestamp, key, value);` missed the header information in the ProducerRecord. Should invoke this like :&lt;/p&gt;

